Package: eCerto
Title: The eCerto package of the Bundesanstalt für Materialforschung und -prüfung (BAM)
Version: 0.1.32
Date: 2022-05-23
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jan", "Lisec", email = "jan.lisec@bam.de", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Frederik", "Kreß", role = "aut"))
Description: The package contains a shiny app which provides various functionality to load, 
    process and backup data for the statistical evaluation of analyses conducted during 
    the production of certified reference materials (CRMs).
